    Afka reer magaaluhu yaqaan waan ka oodnahaye
    Ii-maroojihii bay khatalay kii aan aaminaye
    Afar bawlad laga gooyey bay igu aluubeene
    Anigoo arkaayaa gacmaha laygu iibsadaye
